channel.description:
HYDRANS x Mr Mooo - Antithesis *headphones recommended*
This was a collab with @Mr_Mooo Had a lot of fun working with him!
[Click here ](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans/antithesis) [Or here (My SoundCloud)](https://soundcloud.com/hydrans) [Mr Mooo's Soundcloud](https://soundcloud.com/mr_mooo)
![insLP|500x500](https://sjc6.discourse-cdn.com/standard10/uploads/auxy/optimized/2X/5/511da6769e92f5a7194b989bc1cc1f6bad6740c5_1_500x500.jpeg)
(album art made with [canva.com](http://canva.com/))
Any feedback is appreciated! This is the sixth track in my upcoming LP. Make sure to listen to the other tracks as well!
